name: Yeet it over
description:
Yeet it over is a simple and a hard platformer where the player only control the character with their mouse only.

  • Has 20 level with some stages is easier depending on player
  • 15+ unique music for each level
  • auto save system 
  • Easy to understand game.

Debuking:Programmer,Game Designer.

RTHiro:Artist.

Takojoe:Musician.

If there is any bugs please state in the comment.

We will update the game as much as we can.
